Package: primeDB
Type: Package
Title: R Client for PRIME Database API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Zhizhuo", "Zhang", email = "zhangzhizhuo@sjtu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for accessing the PRIME (PRIME Database) microbiome data through its RESTful API. 
    This package provides functions to retrieve project metadata, sample information, 
    taxonomic data, abundance data, and statistical analyses from the PRIME database.
    The package supports both Silva 138.2 and Greengenes2 2024.09 reference databases.
